Forget about stumbling in the dark, looking for something in a drawer or cupboard that you can’t find because you can’t see a thing, or even going to the bathroom without waking up anyone on your way. They’re just perfect for: wardrobes, drawers, cupboards, corridors, bedrooms, kitchens, bathrooms, offices, cars, car trucks, camping, you name it.
